ActYukon Act
SubjectRelinquishment of the Administration and Control of Public Real Property from the Commissioner of Yukon
PrecisOrder approving the RELINQUISHMENT by the Commissioner of Yukon to Her Majesty the Queen in right of Canada as represented by the Minister of Indian Affairs and Northern Development, of the administration and control of a parcel of land for housing purposes by the WHITE RIVER FIRST NATION, in the town of Beaver Creek in Yukon.
